<div class="wrap2">
 Press Release: UGA Theatre presents a world-premiere translation of three medieval farces
</div>
<div class="views-field views-field-created">
 <span class="field-content">
  Tuesday, March 5, 2019 - 1:14pm
 </span>
</div>
<div class="views-field views-field-body">
 <div class="field-content">
  <div class="wrap">
   <p>
    <span>
     <span>
     </span>
    </span>
    <span>
     <span>
      <span>
       ATHENS, GA – UGA Theatre presents “Peas, Patelin, and Purgation: Three Farcical Arts of the Deal.” Featuring a world-premiere translation and directed by associate professor Marla Carlson, performances are March 19–23 at 8:00 p.m.…
      </span>
     </span>
    </span>
   </p>
  </div>
 </div>
</div>
<div class="views-row">
 <div class="views-field views-field-title">
